This Five Star Notebook gives you plenty of space to write out notes, ideas, reminders and more no matter where you go. The compact size easily fits in a backpack, gym bag or purse. KEEP IT ALL TOGETHER Our pockets are tough enough to handle all your notes. Reinforced pockets help prevent tears and keep papers organized, giving you one less thing to stress about.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 9, 2018
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Yes!! Five Star Spiral Notebooks, 1 Subject, 7" x 5", Teal, Yellow, Lime, 3 Pack
reviews.reviewText: These are great little casual notebooks. I bought them to scribble daily notes on one specific subject.They won't be notebooks I'll keep, as a personal journal or a Bullet Journal might be. Maybe I'll rip some pages out, maybe I'll transcribe or file some pages, but nothing has to be perfect or beautiful. They're mostly notebooks to use and discard.So as "just a notebook," these work for me. Here are features I like:*Spiral binding means pages can be ripped out easily*There's a little perforation next to the spiral, so pages can be taken out neatly if desired.*The covers are just firm enough, and just flexible enough*The two little pockets in the front, one of my favorite features*Bright, pretty colors*College ruling*100 pages, just enough, but not too bulky* 5" x 7" is a great purse size.*The price is right
